name: Air Canada Rouge A319-114 [C-FZUG] INAUGURAL landing in Calgary ᴴᴰ
description:
My first time seeing Air Canada Rouge! :D

This is the inaugural flight of Air Canada's Rouge subsidiary operating the Las Vegas to Calgary route, using the flight numbers RV1897 (LAS-YYC) and RV1896 (YYC-LAS). Sorry for the lousy viewpoint, I was expecting the plane to land on another runway. I hope you enjoy the video, nonetheless, and watch in 1080p for better quality!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
